I’ve Told Buhari About My 2023 Presidential Ambition – Tinubu
0 Comments
1 Day Ago “The other time the President complained that age is telling on him, that if he works for some hours, he becomes exhausted. Should a very complex nation like Nigeria be ruled by such people that age is not on their side? Nigeria is a very complex nation, and this country can give a young man a headache. “Age is a factor in ruling a complex nation like Nigeria because you will be thinking of so many things, you will be thinking of your family, constituency, the entire country with more than 300 ethnic nationalities, you are thinking about international issues, the economy. Look at Obama; within one year, he grew gray hair. “The Presidency; we need should be a young, dynamic person with the energy to move around. Look at Buhari with all the killings in his state; he can’t move around because age is not on his side. He may be mentally sound, but he’s physically comatose.



